1. *Pored* mene sedi njegova sestra. (Beside me sits his sister.)
2. *Poredili* smo se po boji kosulje. (We lined up according to shirt color.)
3. *Poredak* je ispravljen pre vremena. (The order was corrected ahead of time.)
4. *Poredio* sam svoje knjige po godini izdavanja. (I sorted my books by year of release.)
5. Nisam *poredila* njegovu i moju verziju. (I did not compare his and my version.)